title: Tkinter GUI ApplicationDevelopment HOTSHOT [PDF]
description:
2013 | 362 Pages | ISBN: 1849697949 |PDF | 3 MB

Tkinter is the built-in GUI package that comes with standard python distributions. 

This means it is easy to get started right away, without any extra installation or configuration. 

Tkinters strength lies in its simplicity of use and its intuitive nature which makes it suited for programmers and non-programmers alike. 

Once you get started, you will be surprised to see how a few lines of code can produce powerful GUI applications.
